<!-- §8 Why people are buying — problem this solves -->
<h2>What Problems Does This Solve?</h2>
<p>Travel sleep is hard. Hotel noise, snoring seatmates, and unfamiliar rooms keep you awake. Full-size sound machines are too bulky to pack. And running out of battery mid-sleep defeats the whole purpose. The Restnature solves all three by fitting in a pocket while delivering 16 sounds, all-night battery, and easy USB-C charging.</p>
