      <tr><td>Running out of battery mid-sleep on portable devices</td><td>USB-C rechargeable with all-night battery life; also works plugged in</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- §9 What is [Product]? -->
<h2>What Is the Restnature White Noise Machine?</h2>
<p>The Restnature is a palm-sized white noise machine built for travelers and small spaces. At just under 2 inches tall and 0.1 pounds, it's genuinely portable — you can clip it to a keychain or toss it in a carry-on. It plays 16 different sounds (7 nature sounds, 3 white noise variations, 3 fan sounds, and 3 lullabies), offers 32 volume levels for precision control, charges via USB-C, and includes timer modes (30/60/90 minutes or continuous). A full charge lasts 6-8 hours depending on volume.</p>

