<div class="faq supporting-questions">
  <div class="faq-item"><h3>How loud does the Restnature white noise machine get?</h3><p>Plenty loud for a hotel room or bedroom — the 32 volume levels give fine control. It won't fill a large open-plan space, but it's more than adequate for personal use within 6-8 feet.</p></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><h3>How long does the battery last?</h3><p>On a full charge, expect 6-8 hours of continuous play depending on volume. It charges via USB-C in about 2 hours and works plugged in as well.</p></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><h3>Is it good for babies?</h3><p>Yes — it includes 3 lullaby sounds specifically for babies, plus the white noise and nature sounds work well for nurseries. The small size makes it easy to clip to a stroller or place in a crib area.</p></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><h3>Does it have a headphone jack?</h3><p>No — this is a speaker-only device. If you want personal audio while sleeping, pair it with our Bluetooth Sleep Mask instead.</p></div>
